Streaming string sort is designed to sort large string data on heterogeneous
multicore architectures. Fast and effcient string sort on GPU is used to sort
the strings and the string data is streamed from the CPU to the GPU, when
needed. We provide results on benchmark datasets and datasets designed to
demonstrate scalability to large data size.
